# Other coding agents' local context — keep private, same as CLAUDE.md.
# (gitignore has no inline-comment syntax; keep each pattern on its own line.)
# AGENTS.md = Codex / OpenAI (also the cross-tool standard)
# GEMINI.md = Google Gemini CLI · KIMI.md = Kimi / Moonshot · QWEN.md = Qwen Code
AGENTS.md
GEMINI.md
KIMI.md
QWEN.md
